Package: KaroSpaceR
Title: Build KaroSpace-Like Viewers from RDS Inputs
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Langseth", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Standalone R-side exporter for spatial transcriptomics objects
    stored as RDS files. The package normalizes supported R objects into the
    viewer payload expected by the vendored KaroSpace viewer shell and writes
    a standalone HTML viewer without depending on the KaroSpace repository at
    runtime.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: false
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    methods
Suggests:
    Matrix,
    SingleCellExperiment,
    SpatialExperiment,
    SummarizedExperiment
